{"tid":1305620,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"整左薑蔥抄蟹","createTime":"2019-07-11T01:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T05:59:06.000Z","uid":130138,"like":68,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"bf3ac78f0f640dbdf191d80c067c29192422eb10","tid":1305620,"uid":130138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:58:54.000Z","msg":"首先 用水沖一沖啲蟹 因為佢身上既毛都會好污衊 有泥 最好用牙刷刷一刷先<br />\n之後就斬左兩個蟹拑落黎先(廢事俾佢夾親)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OrFz6oz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOrFz6oz.png&h=fdd21f3b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TH13ZJA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTH13ZJA.png&h=cfb3b09b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j2AcS3C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj2AcS3C.png&h=9191bee4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n斬蟹就係佢中間斬落去<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/COyxS4z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCOyxS4z.png&h=6e6a036c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n啡色既一條條要meet左佢 唔食既<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X6pw8Dm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX6pw8Dm.png&h=db0ab8b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蟹拑同其他蟹手腳可以亨碎少少方便之後食 之後就每塊放小小生粉<br />\n切好蔥薑蒜 就可以準備走油<br />\n放生粉同走油可以防止蟹膏抄既時候散(雖然我隻蟹冇咩膏)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LexOrq2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLexOrq2.png&h=e5c97f47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就可以落鑊走油喇 油熱之後加幾片薑 再落蟹件<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/83yxS61.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F83yxS61.png&h=b172b886&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n走哂油之後拎起蟹件放係旁邊 倒走啲油<br />\n<br />\n之後重新落油 抄一抄薑蔥蒜 等啲味出一出先<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/11/095356_ab37703f23bbfc6b5167511995be035c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F11%2F095356_ab37703f23bbfc6b5167511995be035c.png&h=91a97361&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再落翻啱啱走過油既蟹入去抄<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hOjEx7T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhOjEx7T.png&h=1682cdc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n抄一陣之後加水 等佢滾 再加蠔油同鹽調味<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BzBPaUP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBzBPaUP.png&h=ff7ff9c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就上得碟!!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EKqHvVg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEKqHvVg.png&h=44285ae2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n是日晚餐重整左麻辣皮蛋 分享一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sg7KKfD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsg7KKfD.png&h=bc817f10&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7179967bbe25b5c45bdf42f9e43a334212722b0e","tid":1305620,"uid":254384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:01:46.000Z","msg":"jeng"},{"pid":"8364b45db29537ba785486e7793d5de97b338bd9","tid":1305620,"uid":30831,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:03:17.000Z","msg":"正皮比皮蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n皮蛋啲汁點整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c93689d8948421b3af5e95f1bab511f5e8fec13b","tid":1305620,"uid":130138,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"8364b45db29537ba785486e7793d5de97b338bd9","tid":1305620,"uid":30831,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:03:17.000Z","msg":"正皮比皮蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n皮蛋啲汁點整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /